{"tid":473121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單身多年突然同女神拍拖有感","createTime":"2017-11-19T01:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T11:28:41.000Z","uid":113807,"like":169,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf5d2005d2c5d70f4136f1070adbee1a5eed2c9","tid":473121,"uid":113807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T01:55:28.000Z","msg":"我真係好唔慣...同女神bb拍拖已經就快2個月 我當初以為佢真係女神 原來都只不過係普通女人 只要個男人對佢好 咩都唔介意 佢成日都話唔可以冇左我 其實我知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢鍾意我好 但佢冇同屋企人講同我拍拖 反而我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得佢唔想公開個關係 但佢又肯同我搞野 錫錫同攬攬 仲plan左年頭去旅行 我知我事業仲未算成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢只係想暫時有個男人錫佢 比安全感佢 將來如果我冇成就，佢就會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我一定會起佢走之前扑多幾次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                     <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾真係唔好拍拖，就算拍到都只會好似玩地下情咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce37ac46a615cf32a9b0ef8eb394e78dc12ffe31","tid":473121,"uid":77484,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T01:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba65501a44c8f95f03357d6fdedaf76fef638724","tid":473121,"uid":9104,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"正評樓主有自知之明"},{"pid":"e9f9eb1a47e42701330d830c552dca0a4a17c179","tid":473121,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"埋單"},{"pid":"edd7ab335061eedf41941dd943e4d6d3a653573a","tid":473121,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"扑多野先 中出"},{"pid":"08e5847813aec6